    Pin connections
    Name      Arduino     MAX7219 7 Segment display
    -----------------------------------------------
              +5V         VCC
              GND         GND
    DIN       D11/MOSI    DIN
    CS        D10/SS      CS
    CLK       D13/SCK     CLK

    Speaker   D7          -

